{"tid":1696945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈唔應該改名","createTime":"2019-11-06T13:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T14:21:19.000Z","uid":281401,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c40f73feafb45c6c2d74062a5a166a9a3341b9b3","tid":1696945,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"有人話<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span></strong>好容易令人有另外一種既解讀，指<em><del>色情</del></em>。<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得色情係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">以前</span></span>既定義，係屬於<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">舊時代</span></span>既解讀。<br />\n<br />\n黃色本身係唔同既地方，都有好多種唔同既解讀，可以係自由主義者，可以係台灣政黨時代力量既顏色，亦可以象徵希望&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2014年同2019年，香港人已經賦予<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黃色</strong></span>一個嶄新既意義：<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span></strong><br />\n代表每一個離開既手足<br />\n代表每一個有良知既人<br />\n代表所有認同香港價值既真‧香港人</div><br />\n<br />\n我希望手足唔好作繭自縛，陷入一個怕人誤解既思維陷阱，去斬腳指避沙蟲，去諗改咩名，點改好會更加好。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">其實點樣改都唔會更加好<br />\n<br />\n我哋應該更加著力於點樣<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推廣同宣傳</span></strong></span>呢個黃色既全新理念</div><br />\n<br />\n好似紅色，你會諗起共產黨；藍色，你會諗起國民黨；綠色，你會諗起民進黨<br />\n我希望<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黃色</strong></span>以後係全世界多一個意義，以後會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">代表我哋呢個陣營，一個香港人既反共陣營</span></span>"},{"pid":"bca6e9756884d380355bb62bdbdde394217f13e9","tid":1696945,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"想參加罷工，但又驚冇左份工？輪更制幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要人！制更制！日日炒經濟！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696258</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"573356d7a1d8088a200c6782de4910f2932b35ec","tid":1696945,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"同意，基本上聽到 「黃店」呢兩個字都唔會聯想到第二個意思<br />\n相反，有史以來，邊有色情店鋪會大大聲叫自己做「黃店」？<br />\n<br />\n所以黃色經濟圈無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df9d3d54d7f00ac150e398ac3595381da388ceb","tid":1696945,"uid":331459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:51:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">P牌廢中推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足幫幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布《我愛美貨》行動開始！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696942</a>"},{"pid":"d49d85b5bf6669dc1ed19813e5d8660218c16af3","tid":1696945,"uid":93932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"黃金經濟圈"},{"pid":"e4e23ba0f5c32cee3d2e3b317317074f7f80ecfe","tid":1696945,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d49d85b5bf6669dc1ed19813e5d8660218c16af3","tid":1696945,"uid":93932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"黃金經濟圈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"我之前都支持用呢個名，但細想之後發覺根本冇呢個需要。<br />\n<br />\n我哋已經賦予黃色一個全新既意義"},{"pid":"a98d783557ef93bc0bb2f74f7db77cef64cd1cba","tid":1696945,"uid":336462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:21:19.000Z","msg":"你願意為被捕人士同失去眼睛和生命的手足爭取公義嗎！<br />\n你又願意為公義冒險ma !<br />\n<br />\n@vvovv2019"}]}